# Nexus Command Center environment variables
# Copy to .env.local for local dev. In production set these in the Vercel project.
# Never commit real secrets.

# Supabase (Step 2 and 2.5). Anon/publishable key is safe to expose; access is gated
# by Supabase Auth plus RLS. No service_role key is used.
